<html>
    <%- include('head'); -%>
    <body>
        <div class="form_wrapper">
            <form action="/cart" method="POST">
                <button>Go Back</button>
            </form>
            <div>
                <p>Important Notice</p>
                A confirmation email with an Order Number & the total amount (including shipping fees) will be sent to you within 24 hours once your order is placed.<br>
                <br>
                Payment via <br>
                Manual Banking (ATM transfer / Cash Deposit)<br>
                Internet Banking (Online Transfer / Interbank Transfer)<br>
                 <br>
                Make your payment to<br>
                Maybank 111186209854<br>
                Esther Sim <br>
                 <br>
                Payment update:<br>
                Please update us your payment by taking a clear snapshot of your Manual Banking receipt<br>
                or screenshot of your Internet Banking receipt together with your Order Number<br>
                [ EG: receipt + Order Number (#10000) ]<br>
                 <br>
                Email – littletwenty.store@gmail.com<br>
                IG Direct Message -  @littletwenty.store<br>
                <br>
                Note:<br>
                Please make your payment and sent us the receipt within 48hrs once order has been confirmed.<br>
